  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">High level project plan</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Data &amp; More has a standard best practice method/project plan and base configuration of the solution that makes it easy to roll out the compliance solution. </h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><p>Below is an overview of the high level project plan.</p>\n<p>First step is an IT infrastructure meeting to enable the solution to work in your infrastructure</p>\n<p>Second step the startup phase (kick off meeting) with a walkthrough of the solution and the project team will as a trial receive a live clean-up report on their own data and compliance reporting on the over all data. In workshop #1 and #2 we will go through the process and go through the clean-up reports the project team has recieved and recap the standard configuratino and setup.</p>\n<p>After this we will scan and send out clean-up reports one source at a time. Before each send out of the clean-up report there is a short status meeting.</p>\n<p>For each new source to be added, there is also a \"custodian mapping\" meeting where you review who the recipients of the cleanup reports are for the non-compliant data that exists where there is no natural responsible.</p>\n<p>Data &amp; More will continuously as part of the operation monitor the solution and trim false positives, based on the feedback from the end users.</p>\n<p>All meetings with agenda, purpose of the meeting and what the customer should do is explaind in detail here in the support site.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://hubs.ly/Q03lzwD-0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here is a link to our standard implementation presentation in pdf</a></p>\n<p><strong>Below is an overview of the high level project plan.</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"363\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png?width=688&amp;height=363&amp;name=image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png\" width=\"688\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png?width=344&amp;height=182&amp;name=image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png?width=688&amp;height=363&amp;name=image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png?width=1032&amp;height=545&amp;name=image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png?width=1376&amp;height=726&amp;name=image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png?width=1720&amp;height=908&amp;name=image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png?width=2064&amp;height=1089&amp;name=image-png-May-08-2025-08-50-45-6656-AM.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<br>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
